lead_paragraph: The Waikato Chiefs have tied down 21-year-old exciting prospect Damian McKenzie for another two years in a major coup for the twice Super Rugby champions.

headline.print_headline: Chiefs Beaming After 'Smiling Assassin' McKenzie Inks Deal
